{"tid":980715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜特爾特︰天主教教會應該俾啲神父搵男朋友 反正佢地大部份都係gay佬","createTime":"2019-01-13T17:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T12:53:26.000Z","uid":89046,"like":89,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"196b285fee3203b0ee8a06072e2f651bc144070a","tid":980715,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>'Most of them are gay': Rodrigo Duterte calls on the Catholic Church to allow its &lsquo;useless&rsquo; priests to have boyfriends</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6580715/amp/Rodrigo-Duterte-calls-Catholic-Church-allow-useless-priests-boyfriends.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6580715%2Famp%2FRodrigo-Duterte-calls-Catholic-Church-allow-useless-priests-boyfriends.html&d=omOpuDpu%2BCskMQmwPHXVB7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=ddf3cc95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6580715/amp/Rodrigo-Duterte-calls-Catholic-Church-allow-useless-priests-boyfriends.html</a><br />\n<br />\nBy George Martin For mailonline<br />\n08:51 11 Jan 2019, updated 09:14 11 Jan 2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- Duterte made the comments at a groundbreaking ceremony in Manila on Friday <br />\n- The Filipino President has previously said 'almost 90 per cent' of priests are gay <br />\n- Last month he also called on citizens to 'kill' priests in a speech at his palace </strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFilipino President Rodrigo Duterte has called on the Catholic Church to allow priests to have boyfriends.<br />\n<br />\nIn a shocking speech given at a groundbreaking ceremony for a school near the capital Manila on Friday Duterte claimed 'most priests are gay' as he doubled down on a previous claim that 'almost 90 per cent' of the clergy are homosexuals. <br />\n<br />\n'Only I can say bishops are sons of b*****s, damn you. That is true. Most of them are gay,' he said.<br />\n<br />\n'They should come out in the open, cancel celibacy and allow them to have boyfriends.'<br />\n<br />\nDuterte, who is a practicing Catholic, has previously spoken openly about his childhood abuse at the hands of a priest.<br />\n<br />\nIt comes just a month after Duterte said in a speech at the Presidential Palace in the Phillippines that Catholic priests are 'useless fools' who should be 'killed'.  <br />\n<br />\nDuterte's strong remarks are believed to have been made in response to the Catholic church's opposition to his government's ongoing war on drugs, which has left thousands dead.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38881249bdc00b4a7c5c1bbc5fa36f7a7babfc19","tid":980715,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T17:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7370aafd844ff407ca8e13a4ad20ff0a219c503","tid":980715,"uid":132896,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;Only I can say bishops are sons of b*****s, damn you.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n痴線佬"},{"pid":"66504a47aa6efc7527cdc53a018cef0ef11de538","tid":980715,"uid":75406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T18:47:03.000Z","msg":"仲有細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d47b68243b729f8b931ffa25ee6578fb5157c65","tid":980715,"uid":89046,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T23:42:39.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特：誰能證明上帝存在我就辭職<br />\n2018/7/8 明報<br />\n<br />\n一向言論惹火的菲律賓總統杜特爾特上月底公開質疑「原罪說」還稱「上帝愚蠢」，言論在菲律賓這個天主教徒佔多數的國家，引起眾怒。杜特爾特上周五再挑戰教徒，說如果他們能證明上帝存在，就馬上辭職。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓《星報》報道，杜特爾特周五在達沃市出席活動時說：「你今天去做，只要有一個人能見到上帝並和他交談，數億人中我只需要一人。如果有這麼一個人，女士們，先生們，我會立即宣布辭職。」杜特爾特之後又批評神職人員收奉獻：「如果你真的在幫助別人，你還為什麼要向他們要錢？」<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特早前援引《聖經》，稱上帝允許試探破壞自己的受造物簡直是「愚蠢」，又挑戰「原罪」教義，稱上帝將人類從未同意去犯的罪強加給人類。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特發表這些言論，但他聲稱自己不是無神論者，並相信有一種精神控制宇宙。有杜特爾特的盟友批評他的「上帝愚蠢」論，有主教更稱他為精神病患者。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特不斷發表針對天主教言論，其中一個原因是天主教會堅決反對人工節育，令希望推行計劃生育的他不滿。去年1月，杜特爾特發布行政命令，指示機構資助和執行計劃生育，確保免費提供計劃生育用品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180708/s00005/1531028153554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180708%2Fs00005%2F1531028153554&d=omOpuDpu%2BCskMQmwPHXVB7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=edc38deb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180708%2Fs00005%2F1531028153554&h=86e97c99\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180708/s00005/1531028153554</a>"},{"pid":"df38b71e2670dd1b7e294b9406a0ed0cd4c5a30b","tid":980715,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T23:44:40.000Z","msg":"痴線總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97ac3f39a1a043b84d7d09253fcf4fc52aa3748","tid":980715,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T23:51:05.000Z","msg":"痴媽根架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm